entry.content:
The ten designs comprising the Skull series by Preacher were originally designed to be painted by hand onto fabric. The owner of each of the NFTs in this series is granted an exclusive copyright license to produce clothing featuring this artwork, subject to the Non-fungible Token Agreement, limited to a maximum of 1,000 clothing applications per year.
